      },
      "date": "2012-07-05 08:05:41.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 10:\n\nIn the patch there is no sanity test associated. Initially we added a restripe of empty file test for this (inside a client or between 2 clients) and it triggered many bugs.\nAs layout lock is not mandatory unless we use file migration or HSM, in case of bug, it would be good to have a way to disable it. In the patch here is no more a way to disable the layoutlock from /proc, should be good to re-introduce it",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 10
    },
